/*  
==============================================
FFF Light 2.0 - a vBulletin mod for the FFF
==============================================
Created by LukeLC (aka Kirito) 03/2014
======================================
ABOUT:
======
The original FFF Light modified the new bTech 
Blue theme on the FFF with a lighter color
scheme that was easy on the eyes but also
coordinated nicely with brighter font colors.
It was functional, but made no attempt at being
aesthetically pleasing.

FFF Light 2.0 takes a different approach,
instead restricting font colors in favor of an
improved overall design that is even brighter
and more pleasant to use than the original
bTech Light. Its goal is to be a total
overhaul rather than a simple mod, the sort of
skin that can be used on a full-time basis.


=========
FEATURES:
=========
v2.1
-Several little bugfixes

v2.0
-Total overhaul
-Animation on certain links and buttons
-Some minor pages are incomplete, but all *should* be usable. 

v1.1
-Some general touchup
-Updated Shoutbox

v1.0
-Covers all main pages of the FFF, including moderation tools
-Corrects image slider clipping and awkward element positioning
-Adds full header banner (even where bTech currently does not)
-Corrects minor positioning errors present within bTech itself
-KNOWN ISSUES: 
    "New Posts" section and keyword searches generate glitched-out
    threads. 
    Some "Community" pages are not yet fully modified; still usable.
    Some miscellaneous elements are not yet properly aligned; usable.

=============
VERSION INFO:
=============
You are using: v2.1

This mod is subject to updates
*/

@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);
@-moz-document domain("finalfantasyforums.net") {

/* FONT COLORS */

    /*greens*/
    *[color="#00ff00"], *[color="#F0FFFF"], *[color="#F0FFF0"], *[color="#99ffcc"] {
        color:#009900 !important;
    }
    
    /*oranges*/
    *[color="orange"], *[color="#daa520"], *[color="#ffff00"], *[color="#fff0f5"], *[color="#FAEBD7"], *[color="#FFFFE0"], *[color="#ffffcc"], *[color="#ffff99"], *[color="#ffff66"] {
        color:#cc6622 !important;
    }
    
    /*blues*/
    *[color="#00ffff"], *[color="#F0F8FF"], *[color="#E6E6FA"], *[color="#AFEEEE"], *[color="#ADD8E6"], *[color="#00ffff"], *[color="#ccffff"], *[color="#ccccff"], *[color="#40e0d0"] {
        color:#00aacc !important;
    }    
    
    /*grays*/
    *[color="white"], *[color="#FFFFFF"], *[color="#d3d3d3"], *[color="#cccccc"] {
        color:#666 !important;
    } 
    
    /*purples*/
    *[color="#DDA0DD"] {
